race.comment: ZOUCRATIC (8) returned from a six-month spell in good order last start, racing near the pace then boxing on well for a 1.2 length defeat over 1200m at Kembla. Has come back in far better shape this prep and with further natural improvement a win is on the cards. MARIKO (1) met with solid support on debut last start over 900m at this track but found one far better. Sure to be competitive again with this step up in trip. ADEEL IT'S A STEAL (2) resumes. Didn't fire at his only appearance back on 12 April but won a recent trial so might have more to offer this prep. THREE ARROWS (7) debuts. Trials in readiness for this have been excellent.
